title: Nas Daily: Facebook Creator to $11 Million Dollar Entrepreneur
description: Nuseir Yassin quit his software developer job at Venmo to become a full time vlogger and created 1 minute videos everyday for 1000 days on his Facebook page Nas Daily. He's localized his content to over a dozen languages and has since transitioned into his entrepreneurial journey. Most notably, Nuseir has founded Nas Academy - which recently raised $11 million dollars in a Series A round.
dc:creator: Reed Duchscher and Blake Robbins
